    "longBusinessSummary": "Saigon General Service Corporation engages in services and trading, real estate, and financial services businesses in Vietnam. It operates through four segments: Sales, Automobile Services, Real Estate Business, and Financial Activity. The company is involved in the trading, distribution, repair, and maintenance of automobiles, motorbikes, and spare parts; trading of jewelry and construction materials; provision of hotel and restaurant services; trading of real estate and land use rights; leasing of warehouses, offices, commercial centers, and workshops; and investing in and developing real estate projects, such as office buildings, apartments, villas, and resorts. It also offers consulting, real estate brokerage, e-commerce, travel, and advertising services, as well as software publishing and other services related to information technology; invests in trading and services, real estate, and infrastructure businesses; and operates business centers. Saigon General Service Corporation was formerly known as District 1 Service Company and changed its name to Saigon General Service Corporation in January 1996. The company was founded in 1982 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
